### Home
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/

###

### Get All Courses
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses

###

### Create Course
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Python Programming",
    "code": "CS102",
    "credits": 3
}

###

### Get Course by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/courses/1

###

### Get All Students
GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/students

###

### Create Student
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Alice",
    "email": "alice@example.com"
}

###

### Enroll Student
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/students/1/enroll
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "course_id": 1
}